window.docContents[174].resolve({"/The-Type-System/Quotients/#equivalence-relations":{"contents":"等价关系是自反、对称和传递的关系。\n\nEquivalence Relations根据类型的某些规范等价关系的等价性是使用 ≈ 编写的，它是使用 类型类 HasEquiv 重载的。\n\nHasEquiv α is the typeclass which supports the notation x ≈ y where x y : α.x ≈ y says that x and y are equivalent. Because this is a typeclass,\nthe notion of equivalence is type-dependent.Conventions for notations in identifiers:* The recommended spelling of ≈ in identifiers is equiv.\n\n\n\n关系 r 实际上是等价关系，这一事实被声明为 Equivalence r。\n\nAn equivalence relation r : α → α → Prop is a relation that is* reflexive: r x x,* symmetric: r x y implies r y x, and* transitive: r x y and r y z implies r x z.Equality is an equivalence relation, and equivalence relations share many of the properties of\nequality.An equivalence relation is reflexive: r x xAn equivalence relation is symmetric: r x y implies r y xAn equivalence relation is transitive: r x y and r y z implies r x z\n\n\n\n每个 Setoid 实例都会导致一个对应的 HasEquiv 实例。\n\n\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009Type System\u0009商数","header":"4.5.3. 等价关系","id":"/The-Type-System/Quotients/#equivalence-relations"}});